# Documentation Structure

**Single index:** `docs/README.md`

```text
docs/vision/      assumptions, target architecture, binding decisions
docs/reference/   as-implemented (module map, flows, module docs)
docs/planning/    roadmap, status, sprints
docs/adr/         why decisions were frozen
```

Folder READMEs are **catalogs only** — not second indexes.

## Layers

| Layer | Folder | Update when |
|-------|--------|-------------|
| Index | `docs/README.md` | New category or folder |
| Onboarding | `onboarding/DEVELOPER_GUIDE.md` | Setup/tooling only |
| Vision | `docs/vision/` | Principles, binding decisions, target design |
| Reference | `docs/reference/` | Merged wave; contract change |
| Progress | `planning/CURRENT_STATUS.md` | Sprint milestone |
| Planning | `planning/sprints/` | Sprint planning — not impl status |
| ADRs | `docs/adr/` | Durable decisions |

## Reference (as-implemented)

| File | Owns |
|------|------|
| `reference/MODULE_MAP.md` | Packages, status |
| `reference/DATA_WORKFLOWS.md` | Data movement, diagrams |
| `reference/modules/*.md` | Per-module implemented detail |

Do not duplicate in `DEVELOPER_GUIDE.md` or sprint files.

## Single Source of Truth

- **Built?** `src/`, tests, then `reference/` — not `vision/` or roadmap alone.
- **Should be?** `vision/`, `planning/`, ADRs.
- **Why?** ADRs + binding decision docs in `vision/`.

`vision/ANALYSIS_WORKSPACE_AND_DERIVED_DATA.md` wins on MA derived-data conflicts.

## Mandatory Updates

**After merged wave:** `MODULE_MAP.md`; `DATA_WORKFLOWS.md` if paths changed.

**Contract change:** `reference/modules/*`, vision if binding decision changed, tests, ADR if durable.

**Sprint close:** `CURRENT_STATUS.md`, expand module guides.

## What Not to Do

- No implementation status from vision docs alone.
- No flow diagrams in `DEVELOPER_GUIDE.md` — use `DATA_WORKFLOWS.md`.
- No duplicate indexes in folder READMEs.

## Reading Order

- **Humans:** `docs/README.md` → `DEVELOPER_GUIDE.md` → `reference/` → `vision/` as needed.
- **Agents:** `AGENTS.md` → `CURRENT_STATUS.md` → `vision/` → `reference/` → contracts/tests.
